{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KydPLQptg88AVMfxUvCLBr","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Story {{epic_num}}.{{story_num}}: {{story_title}}\n     2→\n     3→Status: ready-for-dev\n     4→\n     5→<!-- Note: Validation is optional. Run validate-create-story for quality check before dev-story. -->\n     6→\n     7→## Story\n     8→\n     9→As a {{role}},\n    10→I want {{action}},\n    11→so that {{benefit}}.\n    12→\n    13→## Acceptance Criteria\n    14→\n    15→1. [Add acceptance criteria from epics/PRD]\n    16→\n    17→## Tasks / Subtasks\n    18→\n    19→- [ ] Task 1 (AC: #)\n    20→  - [ ] Subtask 1.1\n    21→- [ ] Task 2 (AC: #)\n    22→  - [ ] Subtask 2.1\n    23→\n    24→## Dev Notes\n    25→\n    26→- Relevant architecture patterns and constraints\n    27→- Source tree components to touch\n    28→- Testing standards summary\n    29→\n    30→### Project Structure Notes\n    31→\n    32→- Alignment with unified project structure (paths, modules, naming)\n    33→- Detected conflicts or variances (with rationale)\n    34→\n    35→### References\n    36→\n    37→- Cite all technical details with source paths and sections, e.g. [Source: docs/<file>.md#Section]\n    38→\n    39→<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-START:story-verification -->\n    40→## Verification Requirements\n    41→\n    42→- [ ] Showboat proof document created (`docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.proof.md`)\n    43→- [ ] All acceptance criteria verified with real-world evidence\n    44→- [ ] Test coverage meets target (100%)\n    45→\n    46→## Documentation Requirements\n    47→\n    48→- [ ] Relevant AGENTS.md files updated (list modules touched)\n    49→- [ ] Exec-plan created in `docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.md`\n    50→\n    51→## Testing Requirements\n    52→\n    53→- [ ] Unit tests written for all new/changed code\n    54→- [ ] Integration tests for cross-module interactions\n    55→- [ ] Coverage target: 100%\n    56→<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:story-verification -->\n    57→\n    58→## Dev Agent Record\n    59→\n    60→### Agent Model Used\n    61→\n    62→{{agent_model_name_version}}\n    63→\n    64→### Debug Log References\n    65→\n    66→### Completion Notes List\n    67→\n    68→### File List\n    69→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01GsivLJk9hNLA39uKm9guob","session_id":"9d3ab825-6dfa-42d3-92d1-28b7bc09852d","uuid":"ff55cb9b-a5cd-40f8-838d-41e79048a00b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:33:21.523Z"}
