'`.\n    42→\n    43→**Verdict:** PASS\n    44→\n    45→## AC #6: Does not return dependency name; falls back to basename\n    46→\n    47→**Test:** `falls back to basename when Cargo.toml has name only in [dependencies]`\n    48→**Evidence:** Given `Cargo.toml` with `[dependencies]\\nname = \"dep-name\"` but no `[package]` section, `getProjectName()` returns `basename(testDir)`, NOT `'dep-name'`.\n    49→\n    50→**Verdict:** PASS\n    51→\n    52→## AC #7: All tests pass with zero regressions\n    53→\n    54→**Evidence:** Full test suite: 3021 tests across 113 files, zero failures. Coverage: 97.06% overall, all 123 files above 80% per-file floor.\n    55→\n    56→**Verdict:** PASS\n    57→\n    58→## Coverage\n    59→\n    60→- **docs-scaffold.ts:** 96.29% statements, 90% branches, 100% functions\n    61→- **Overall:** 97.06% (target: 90%)\n    62→- **Per-file floor:** All 123 files above 80%\n    63→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Y5Vmp4wHswe3FNr3ap85bX","session_id":"9d3ab825-6dfa-42d3-92d1-28b7bc09852d","uuid":"ca999914-e6fb-495c-81c9-34299592bd06","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:41:43.337Z"}
